Source: escrotum
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Opinsys Developers <dev@opinsys.fi>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8)
Standards-Version: 3.9.5
Homepage: https://github.com/Roger/escrotum

Package: escrotum
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python, python-gtk2
Description: Linux screen capture using pygtk, inspired by scrot
 Why? Because scrot has glitches when selection is used in refreshing
 windows.
 .
 Features
   - fullscreen screenshots
   - partial(selection) screenshots
   - window screenshot(click to select)
   - screenshot by xid
   - store the image to the clipboard
 .
